{"tid":1560292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"休班警獲發警棍　民建聯陳克勤 : 早有就不會被斬重傷","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:46:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4e0df8f642c3661e333cd66f75db946fa7d83f","tid":1560292,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"警方昨日（9月10日）起向休班警員派發伸縮警棍，一個月後檢討。<br />\n<br />\n立法會保安事務委員會主席陳克勤今早（9月11日）指，早前有休班警員被斬傷，如有警棍，就不會被斬得如此重傷。 陳克勤在港台節目《千禧年代》中表示，早前有休班警員被斬傷，如有警棍，就不會被斬得如此重傷；又指休班警員獲發警棍有助執法，亦可在心理上達到效果。 <br />\n<br />\n陳克勤又指只要市民不犯罪，警員便毋須使用警棍，因此不會進一步破壞警民關係。<br />\n<br />\n有聽眾致電節目表示，不贊成這項措施，指近期部分警員執法時情緒失控，派發警棍予休班警，等同全天候24小時戒備，對市民來說是恐怖的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-11-2019/55847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-11-2019%2F55847&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=759dc1cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-11-2019/55847</a>"},{"pid":"2f66917a5630f40f5324884420710563b01977ac","tid":1560292,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"陳克勤未獲發棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9449a85f4c50dbb3640094e46170a4063bfab511","tid":1560292,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"真係拎武士刀斬人<br />\n拎警棍有Q用咩"},{"pid":"f771e0330c673e5beb92b3cc05ca77d241884fb1","tid":1560292,"uid":62321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:57:46.000Z","msg":"話時話，斬狗單野無聲無氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc5c6af90b181dc37d64e9d79ab380457e7dc24","tid":1560292,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"On9 要斬你 你扲得切出黎咩 你24小時棍不離手呀<br />\n而且幾條友斬你 你得條棍仔撚有用"},{"pid":"9146dd83948fdf91c4447a3b0493c7ab44137da4","tid":1560292,"uid":209888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"既然唔使用就唔會破壞警民關係，咁不如以後24小時陀槍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43087a226f54b6dc8ed1c90d1bc3463ade0f3ac6","tid":1560292,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"似乎條友以為每次警察被街坊包圍果啲全部係暴徒扮架喎，休班警單拖攞支棍出黎同想自殺其實無乜分別。"},{"pid":"ff7d2d5e34b241233f77cbe83abf68d24c12f980","tid":1560292,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">早前有休班警員被斬傷，如有警棍，就不會被斬得如此重傷</span><br />\n<br />\n對住英語天才陳克勤 (十一哥叫佢李克勤)，唔使用刀嘅，搓his breast啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1cb95615f69c91e29b8e6d3c90d9841078af23","tid":1560292,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"陳克勤想做第三個葉劉嗎？"},{"pid":"4c7f1e26434323fd4f9fe98c1e4cc6c4c9577f72","tid":1560292,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"俾人伏擊有支AK47都無用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有無咁弱智？"},{"pid":"8dc94b01e56f99f5d3b0450968b0021ee486b404","tid":1560292,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"不如早的練詠春一打十？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d012f7b5b8558766272683c621478275937fe8","tid":1560292,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"正義的愛國藍絲，是我們發揮作用的時候。<br />\n我們自發保護休班警員，4人一組地護送他們。<br />\n免受暴徒攻擊。#支持警察 #自發保護警察力量"}]}